supports HTML5 video The Fanar Views Residential Development Project has officially been launched. It is a free-hold residential project. Thus the project is considered to be the first of its kind. The Fanar Views Residential Development Project is located within Hawana Salalah. Additionally, the project offers convivence to its residents. It is within proximity to the Fanar Hotel Residences beach. Read Also Pact for Construction of Sur Industrial City Rubber Powder Production Plant in Oman Signed The project offers a mix of twin and standalone villas. Additionally, a mix of townhouses is also available. The homes are fully serviced and furnished. Also, they are available in one, two, and three-bedroom homes. Furthermore, the project includes private pools overlooking lagoons. It was launched by Muriya, an Oman-based developer. The firm is a joint venture (Jv) between Orascom Development Holding (ODH) and Oman Tourism Development Company. The project aims to offer resort-style living within a developed community. It is located in Hawana Salalah within the Governorate of Dhofar. Commenting on the project, Muriya expressed that the project is open to buyers of all nationalities. Moreover, residents will be close to the Fanar Hotel & Residences and its facilities. These will include the sporting facilities, swimming pool, gym, and beaches alongside the business center. Furthermore, residents will also receive exclusive discounts within the hotel’s restaurants. The Chief Development Officer of Muriya also commented on the Fanar Views residential development project. Seif Elkhouly acknowledged that the Governorate of Dhofar continues to gain standing. More especially, in the real estate market as well as the tourist destination industry. He concluded by stating that the project is a robust investment opportunity as well as a great choice for living.